Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.54,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.39,0:00:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛穿上的鞋  敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.07,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.95,0:01:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.49,0:01:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.43,0:01:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.44,0:01:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣是平常起床的時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的時間…說我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過音夢，妳怎麼在做早餐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.57,0:01:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為平常都是我做的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有睡醒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.71,0:01:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別站在那邊了，請過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又穿成這個樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為穿舊衣服的觸感很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.12,0:02:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這樣就像是\N哥哥一直在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，記得之前也曾經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（#14 小狗式購物）\N竟然又做這種夢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種日子總覺得有不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.62,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳身體狀況又不好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.40,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，狀況不好的是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.47,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個月又透支了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.51,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過賴子應該幫了我們很多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賴子的確很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.22,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我又打破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來也沒有省到多少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是得再節省一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.07,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費的話對爸媽也不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，我可以扣你的零用錢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就沒有其他的選擇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.58,0:03:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事我應該拒絕過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣都不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N我是個會說NO（不）的日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然只有在這個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.76,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得我今天這麼早起\N偶爾就一起上學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像會下雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該換了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過才剛剛決定不能浪費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天就這樣結束啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的班會沒什麼事情要轉達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家別到處遊蕩趕快回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我現在要做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢那傢伙已經回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也趕快回家睡懶覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是美春啊，別嚇我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道朝倉學長現在有空嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空是有空啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那請你陪美春去買東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想找音夢學姊一起去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是音夢學姊丟下美春先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定請朝倉學長代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過音夢真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她有什麼理由\N竟然對可愛的學妹爽約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也沒有跟學姊約好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想來找學姊時她已經走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種麻煩事我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是去找其他人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣都不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我是個會說NO的日本人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來並非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正曆老師也要我多照顧美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.89,0:06:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然她是個機器人\N也不會犯什麼大錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.83,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長\N你在做什麼呢，快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.96,0:06:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都下定決心了\N那就好好陪她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.54,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始上課的鐘聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.68,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,融化在桃色的風中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.69,0:06:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到遙遠的某處去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.83,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我立起課本如此夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收集光的粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓嘆息乘雲而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在校庭一角堅強綻放的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搖曳的樣子好耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.95,0:07:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kiss to me\N輕輕綻放光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.16,0:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請接受我內心的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.30,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chime to you\N將鼓動傳達給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起越過天空向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這隻小狗擺飾好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還要帶我逛多久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不去買妳要買的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有特別要買的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.41,0:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女生就算沒東西要買\N也還是會去逛街的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來音夢也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放著不管她就能逛一整天的街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過像她這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.16,0:08:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本看不出美春是個機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是開心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在旁人的眼中確實如此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這種時候被誰給看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會…很不妙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧美春，走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然要回去呢，朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.36,0:08:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼不願意跟美春在一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.57,0:09:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不願意和妳在一起\N是不願意被別人看到在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次跟真子的事也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.37,0:09:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想又平白被誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.21,0:09:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你走那麼快美春跟不上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿妳沒辦法，來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好像會更加不妙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是歌丸的鈴鐺聲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦，迷路了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.89,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐，芳乃學姊怎麼了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是在人群中走散了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻那傢伙實在太嬌小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌丸，你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀況更加惡化當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其在這裡被小櫻找到\N還不如被當成普通的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春，還是走這邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.85,0:10:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只會在這種時候\N遇到一些不想遇到的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為早上的夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長，請振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在大馬路上吵什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有在吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在陪美春買東西而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在陪美春？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是什麼曖昧的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來音夢學姊也來買東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛好需要一些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過美春跟哥哥的組合\N還真是蠻少見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來美春是在警戒範圍之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊，妳買了些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很詭異喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.11,0:11:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，難道妳只扣我的零用錢\N卻把自己的份留下來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就請給我們看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能看啦，美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是男生用的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰的，該不會是杉並的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是男朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.63,0:12:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到在我不知道的時候\N你有這麼親密的男友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊，這當然是給哥哥的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是哥哥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥那個混帳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.28,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看哥哥的襯衫都舊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是又不是不能穿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然經濟吃緊又何必勉強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.69,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這些是買給哥哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是哥哥的襯衫並不會增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時我會像這樣買新的給哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拿哥哥舊的衣服當睡衣穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為新襯衫硬梆梆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿來當睡衣也不好睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不用穿我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了哥哥的\N其他人的我不敢穿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就穿自己的舊衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿大件一點的比較輕鬆又舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很嚮往電影裡這種情節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我都偷偷換掉你的舊襯衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是無所謂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳有洗乾淨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是有哥哥的味道喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以簡單來說就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.35,0:13:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拐彎抹角藉著哥哥的舊襯衫\N達到節省開銷的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.76,0:13:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為了答謝妳為了家計的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的零用錢買個東西送妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，美春也一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也請妳吃點東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.54,0:14:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.38,0:14:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很謝謝你的好意\N但你陪美春已經很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次就請你們兩位自己去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這附近等你們就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.67,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看妳那麼開心\N還以為妳想要買什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的在這裡買就可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳想要買什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他想買的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得送妳東西就選點別的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望哥哥買這個送我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種100圓的東西自己買啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要哥哥買這個給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說買這個就行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挑個妳喜歡的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，為什麼是左手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.02,0:16:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的夢真的是我的夢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊，朝倉學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.27,0:16:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢學姊，妳買了什麼禮物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我啦，音夢學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.19,0:16:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長，今天很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春真的好開心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕小狗呢\N永遠都那麼天真無邪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會這麼說該不會是想追我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，妳別亂說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，你這一份體貼\N對女生而言可是種罪過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春是個機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.64,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚什麼是談戀愛的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以下一話呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是總集篇喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.96,0:17:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.53,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴音輕響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.97,0:17:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於樹林小道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.45,0:17:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨在飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.45,0:18:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.66,0:18:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛也能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都能在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.63,0:19:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.60,0:20:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海參的小孩是小海參
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的海參 藍色的海參
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生的海…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.00,0:20:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙叫豹紋章魚，有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被咬到有可能會致命，小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.22,0:20:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙叫僧帽水母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被牠刺到可能會毒發致死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙叫安保納貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.73,0:21:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被咬傷只要二到三十分鐘\N就會呼吸困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導致全身麻痺而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是含有劇毒的貝類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.94,0:23:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
